Installation Steps

1.Install Java and Set Up Environment Variables

Download and install JDK 23 or higher.

Set JAVA_HOME and add it to the system PATH.

2.Install Selenium WebDriver

Download Selenium JAR files from the Selenium official website.

Add the JAR files to the projectâ€™s classpath.

3.Download ChromeDriver

Download the compatible version from ChromeDriver official site.

Place it inside the Driver folder in the project directory.

4.Set Up the IDE

Open the project in Eclipse or IntelliJ IDEA.

Add the Selenium JAR files to the build path.

5.Run the Script

Open rappido.java.

Run as a Java application.
